OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772655072
OL,3,C'Nothing to suggest' Noah Donohoe went
OL,4,Cinto water tunnel where body was found
OL,6,FA police officer involved in the
OL,7,Fsearch for Noah Donohoe has said there
OL,8,Fwas "nothing to suggest" the 14-year-
OL,9,Fold had gone into a water tunnel where
OL,10,Fhis body was later found.
OL,12,FSergeant Hutchings, was the lead PolSA
OL,13,F(police search adviser) in the search
OL,14,Ffor Noah in 2020.
OL,16,FHe told an inquest into the
OL,17,Fschoolboy's death he did, however,
OL,18,Fbelieve the teenager was still in the
OL,19,Farea close to where he had last been
OL,20,Fseen in north Belfast.
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@XO]
