CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772655072
OL,3,C'Nothing to suggest' Noah Donohoe went
OL,4,Cinto water tunnel where body was found
OL,6,FThe inquest into the death of the
OL,7,Fschoolboy at Belfast Coroner's Court,
OL,8,Fwhich is being heard with a jury, is
OL,9,Fnow in its sixth week.
OL,11,FNoah's naked body was found in a storm
OL,12,Fdrain tunnel in north Belfast in June
OL,13,F2020, six days after he left home on
OL,14,Fhis bike to meet two friends in the
OL,15,FCavehill area of the city.
OL,17,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,18,Fcause of death was drowning.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772655072
OL,3,C'Nothing to suggest' Noah Donohoe went
OL,4,Cinto water tunnel where body was found
OL,6,FCounsel for the coroner Declan Quinn
OL,7,Fresumed his questioning of Sergeant
OL,8,FHutchings on Wednesday morning.
OL,10,FThe barrister asked the witness about
OL,11,Fwhen he became aware of a culvert
OL,12,Fentrance in Northwood Linear Park and
OL,13,Fhow the decision was made to search
OL,14,Fthe tunnel network.
OL,16,FThe officer had told the jury on
OL,17,FMonday that he had spotted the culvert
OL,18,Fand decided it needed to be searched
OL,19,Fbecause the entrance to it could be
OL,20,Fopened.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772655072
OL,3,C'Nothing to suggest' Noah Donohoe went
OL,4,Cinto water tunnel where body was found
OL,6,FThe barrister read to Mr Hutchings
OL,7,Fevidence given previously to the
OL,8,Finquest by Sean McCarry from Community
OL,9,FRescue Service (CRS).
OL,11,FMr McCarry's evidence said that from
OL,12,Ffive minutes of arriving at the park
OL,13,Fon the Monday night, the day after
OL,14,FNoah disappeared, he was aware of the
OL,15,Fculvert as a potential ingress point
OL,16,Ffor Noah.
OL,18,FMr McCarry's evidence said that he had
OL,19,Fphoned Mr Hutchings to tell him about
OL,20,Fthe culvert when he was off duty on
OL,21,FMonday night.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772655072
OL,3,C'Nothing to suggest' Noah Donohoe went
OL,4,Cinto water tunnel where body was found
OL,6,FMr Quinn said: "The upshot of all of
OL,7,Fthat, Sergeant Hutchings, is that Mr
OL,8,FMcCarry has given evidence to the jury
OL,9,Fthat not only did he inform the PolSA
OL,10,Fof the culvert on the Monday evening,
OL,11,Fbut he informed you particularly, what
OL,12,Fdo you say about that?"
OL,14,FThe officer said he remembered getting
OL,15,Fthe call and being told about Noah's
OL,16,Fbike being found and a stream in the
OL,17,Farea.
OL,19,FHe said he told Mr McCarry that if any
OL,20,Fsearch needed to be done he should
OL,21,Fcontact the officer on duty.
OL,26,@nD@POUtD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772655072
OL,3,C'Nothing to suggest' Noah Donohoe went
OL,4,Cinto water tunnel where body was found
OL,6,FMr Hutchings said he was not aware
OL,7,Fthat members of CRS had entered the
OL,8,Fculvert on Monday.
OL,10,FHe said he had not been expecting to
OL,11,Fsee such a large culvert when he
OL,12,Farrived at the park on Tuesday morning.
OL,14,FHe said: "When I got there I walked
OL,15,Fdown the side of the house. That's
OL,16,Fwhen I saw the culvert and the big
OL,17,Fdrain."
OL,26,@vD@JOUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772655072
OL,3,C'Nothing to suggest' Noah Donohoe went
OL,4,Cinto water tunnel where body was found
OL,6,FMr Hutchings was asked if he would
OL,7,Fhave organised an earlier search of
OL,8,Fthe culvert, had he been aware of it
OL,9,Fon Monday.
OL,11,FHe said: "I would have started the
OL,12,Fball rolling."
OL,14,FThe officer said that on the Wednesday
OL,15,Fmorning there were a number of areas
OL,16,Fbeing searched for Noah, including the
OL,17,Fstorm drain tunnels.
OL,19,FHe said: "The storm drain or the
OL,20,Fculvert, was a very low probability, I
OL,21,Fdid not believe he was in there.
OL,26,@sD@JOUtD@NO]{D@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
